01:03:45.952 --> 01:03:47.480
Hey.

01:03:47.560 --> 01:03:49.311
What time is it?

01:03:49.906 --> 01:03:51.708
It's late.

01:03:53.460 --> 01:03:56.433
- Don't do that. Hey.
- No.

01:03:56.513 --> 01:03:58.268
I tried so hard to be quiet too.

01:03:58.348 --> 01:04:02.506
- It's okay.
- I'm sorry. I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

01:04:02.586 --> 01:04:04.475
Why're you dressed?

01:04:04.755 --> 01:04:06.310
Morning.

01:04:06.690 --> 01:04:10.126
Good morning. Gotta go.

01:04:11.394 --> 01:04:14.116
You don't have to. I'll make breakfast.

01:04:14.196 --> 01:04:15.999
You can eat it in bed.

01:04:18.868 --> 01:04:20.757
Sounds so good.

01:04:20.837 --> 01:04:23.873
- But?
- I can't.

01:04:24.640 --> 01:04:26.910
You can't or you won't?

01:04:33.382 --> 01:04:35.652
Bern, I gotta go now.

01:04:36.786 --> 01:04:38.788
Where? Where you gotta...

01:04:39.755 --> 01:04:41.324
Bern.

01:04:42.625 --> 01:04:44.194
Stop.

01:04:51.984 --> 01:04:53.868
You still wanna do this?

01:04:57.874 --> 01:04:59.697
I just don't even...

01:05:00.277 --> 01:05:02.145
What are you doing?

01:05:04.447 --> 01:05:06.316
I'm asking you.

01:05:07.183 --> 01:05:08.672
Yeah.

01:05:08.752 --> 01:05:10.587
So stay.

01:05:11.487 --> 01:05:12.943
I want you to stay.

01:05:13.023 --> 01:05:16.715
And I'm telling you that I cannot. Okay?

01:05:17.060 --> 01:05:19.262
- Kiss me goodbye.
- No.

01:07:50.846 --> 01:07:53.370
Howdy, ma'am. Anybody helping you?

01:07:53.450 --> 01:07:56.239
I'm staying in room 129.
I booked it this morning.

01:07:56.319 --> 01:07:58.909
Alright. I hope everything's going okay.

01:07:58.989 --> 01:08:03.647
Yeah. There seems to be some
sort of fight next door. 128.

01:08:03.727 --> 01:08:06.162
- A fight?
- I heard screaming.

01:08:07.363 --> 01:08:09.886
Alright. You stay dry, okay?

01:08:09.966 --> 01:08:13.003
Take care, and sorry for the inconvenience.

01:08:35.457 --> 01:08:39.095
- Get off of me!
- Get away from me. Get off me!

01:08:43.066 --> 01:08:45.268
- Shut up!
- No!

01:08:50.073 --> 01:08:52.696
You again. What's the fucking problem now?

01:08:52.776 --> 01:08:54.812
I think you know what the problem is.

01:09:04.252 --> 01:09:07.090
Stop it! Stop it!

01:09:08.157 --> 01:09:12.499
Stop! What the... what the fuck
are you doing? Stop it!

01:09:12.578 --> 01:09:15.618
- You fucker? What are you gonna do now?
- What the fuck are you doing?

01:09:15.698 --> 01:09:20.537
You son of a bitch, I fucking told you!
Don't knock on the door! Fuck you!

01:11:27.229 --> 01:11:29.031
Follow her.

01:11:44.980 --> 01:11:46.516
Fuck.

01:12:00.663 --> 01:12:03.453
Listen, open the door.
Open this door, listen!

01:12:03.533 --> 01:12:06.535
Just fucking open the door. Okay?

01:12:19.722 --> 01:12:22.778
Come on, fuck! Open this fucking door!

01:12:30.459 --> 01:12:32.395
Open this fucking door!

01:13:32.988 --> 01:13:34.790
Fucking hell!

01:15:14.696 --> 01:15:17.547
- Sir, you can't park here.
- What the hell's going on?

01:15:18.327 --> 01:15:19.896
Bern?

01:15:24.833 --> 01:15:27.437
Come here. Come here.

01:15:37.880 --> 01:15:39.255
I got you.

01:17:43.572 --> 01:17:45.128
Hey.

01:17:45.208 --> 01:17:48.898
- I thought you were still at the hospital.
- Yeah, I was.

01:17:48.978 --> 01:17:53.416
I'm going to get over to Bern's, get the
place fixed up before they cut her loose.

01:17:55.784 --> 01:17:59.175
- You've gotta go to school today, Mags.
- No, I don't mind. Let me help.

01:17:59.255 --> 01:18:02.445
Don't let this craziness get in the way
of what you've gotta do. Alright?

01:18:02.525 --> 01:18:05.948
Go on, get your stuff.
I'll give you a ride on the way in.

01:18:06.028 --> 01:18:09.064
- How is she?
- She's getting there.

01:18:09.781 --> 01:18:11.784
When is she coming back home?

01:18:13.101 --> 01:18:14.903
Soon enough.

01:18:15.637 --> 01:18:17.694
I heard she killed one of them, Sam.

01:18:18.374 --> 01:18:20.242
Is that true?

01:18:22.210 --> 01:18:23.832
Yeah.

01:18:23.912 --> 01:18:25.535
Who was it?

01:18:25.615 --> 01:18:28.905
Was just some kid.

01:18:29.085 --> 01:18:32.041
And the other one just got away?
He's still out there?

01:18:32.121 --> 01:18:35.545
Yeah, but he's cut up bad.

01:18:35.625 --> 01:18:38.548
Police know what to look for.
They're gonna search the hospitals.

01:18:38.628 --> 01:18:41.517
He ain't gonna get far. It's gonna be okay.

01:18:41.597 --> 01:18:43.653
Are you okay?

01:18:43.733 --> 01:18:46.656
Yeah. I am.

01:18:46.736 --> 01:18:51.179
Things like this, Mags, you've just...
just gotta let 'em pass through, wait it out.

01:18:53.208 --> 01:18:55.411
Now get your stuff. I'll get the car.

01:19:33.148 --> 01:19:34.950
Hey, pal.

01:19:35.350 --> 01:19:38.174
- Hey, Sam.
- Seen your light on.

01:19:38.254 --> 01:19:40.557
Was wondering if you were up this early.

01:19:41.557 --> 01:19:44.560
- Yeah, it's early.
- Leaving us?

01:19:45.193 --> 01:19:47.971
- Yeah, going home.
- Going back South?

01:19:48.361 --> 01:19:49.898
Yeah.

01:19:51.433 --> 01:19:54.269
Well, it's been nice having you.

01:19:58.894 --> 01:20:01.364
I'll just go ahead and get the rest
of your stuff for you.

01:20:01.444 --> 01:20:03.846
No, no, I'm alright. I don't need help.

01:20:10.285 --> 01:20:11.608
You're bleeding.

01:20:17.125 --> 01:20:22.334
Yep. I got into a little accident yesterday,
a little car accident, but I'm okay.

01:20:22.414 --> 01:20:24.300
You had an accident?

01:20:26.251 --> 01:20:27.770
Yep.

01:20:29.571 --> 01:20:31.277
What are you doing?

01:20:32.273 --> 01:20:33.842
Sam.

01:20:36.044 --> 01:20:37.843
- Hey, Sam.
- Piece of shit.

01:20:40.316 --> 01:20:41.884
Sam!

01:20:43.271 --> 01:20:46.019
- Sam!
- Hey, get back in the room!

01:20:46.099 --> 01:20:47.790
- Get back!
- Sam!

01:23:41.362 --> 01:23:43.171
Put that gun down.

01:23:51.756 --> 01:23:54.643
I'm leaving, Sam. Okay?

01:23:54.953 --> 01:23:57.733
You just... you put it down.

01:23:57.813 --> 01:23:59.615
That thing still shoot?

01:24:01.316 --> 01:24:04.720
Put the gun down, I'm not gonna
say it again, I will shoot you dead.

01:24:05.520 --> 01:24:07.355
That's it.

01:24:08.723 --> 01:24:10.580
I'm out of your hair, okay?

01:24:10.960 --> 01:24:13.549
I'm gonna call this square, Sam,
between me and you.

01:24:13.629 --> 01:24:16.024
- You just...
- But I've got to go.

01:24:16.104 --> 01:24:18.233
Just walk away from the car, alright?
Just walk away...

01:24:18.313 --> 01:24:19.879
- I didn't mean to shoot that man.
- Sam, let him go.

01:24:19.979 --> 01:24:22.314
Hey, you go back in the office! Go back now!

01:24:22.394 --> 01:24:25.340
You should listen to her. Okay?

01:24:26.574 --> 01:24:28.898
I'm not letting you leave.
You just walk away from the car.

01:24:28.978 --> 01:24:31.300
No, no, no. No, no, no.

01:24:31.380 --> 01:24:33.615
- Walk away.
- I can't.

01:24:34.282 --> 01:24:36.816
- I can't. I'm sorry.
- You just...

01:24:37.186 --> 01:24:38.874
- ...stop.
- I can't.

